- Function Sort() does not exists, so cannot be linked when NO_INLINE_STDARG
is set. This must be resolved in Sort Library code. NOTE: This probably has
to be resolved in "New Library..." dialog box of language-amigaos-c package!
Until then we have to compile without NO_INLINE_STDARG set.

